<object id="GUID-63543E64-A3C3-4D23-B2CE-86CB43920AFE" class="- topic/object "><desc class="- topic/desc "><p class="- topic/p ">Rinse Printheads </p></desc><param name="testid" value="046032" class="- topic/param "/><param name="target" value="NIL" class="- topic/param "/><param name="axmodule" value="None" class="- topic/param "/></object> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p "> This test refreshes the ink in the printheads by emptying the printheads as far as possible and fill them again with new ink. This is repeated a number of times and can only be done with 1 printhead at a time. 
</p><note id="GUID-8367753B-E7BB-4817-9ABE-618E7B90FB9E" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Preferably stop the test by selecting printhead 0. When the test is stopped with the stop button or if an error occurs during the test, the engine is put into Cold SDS. De-clamp all printheads before making it warm again. 
</p></note></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-686678F1-A321-4B08-84D3-63C9CD28C7FA.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>SDS</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
